n/support-us/where-does-your-money-go" title="See how your donation saves lives">Learn where your money goes</a></li><li> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/faq/donate-by-bank-transfer-or-cheque" title="Find out how to donate by bank transfer, postal transfer or cheque">Donate by bank transfer</a></li><li><h5 class="h5">OTHER WAYS TO GIVE</h5><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/support-us/fundraising-event" title="By organizing a fundraising event, you will be supporting the essential work of the ICRC.">Organize a fundraising event</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/support-us/audience/bequests-and-legacies" title="">Leave a legacy</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/support-us/audience/friends-icrc" title="">Become a Friend of the ICRC</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/support-us/audience/philanthropy" title="">Make a major gift</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/support-us/audience/foundations" title="">Partner with your foundation or trust</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/support-us/audience/corporate-support" title="Support our work through your company">Corporate partnerships</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/support-us/audience/planned-giving" title="Make a lasting difference to the lives of people affected by armed conflict.">Planned giving</a></li></ul></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="nav-donate nav-link-main-container pull-right hidden-xs hidden-sm"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/donate" class="bg-red nav-link-main">Donate</a></div></div></div></div> </nav></div><div class="region region-content"><div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system"><div class="content"> <section class="clearfix breadcrumb-wrapper theme-brown"><div class="container"><ol class="breadcrumb"><li class="i-arrow-right-after"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en">Home</a></li><li class="i-arrow-right-after"><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law">War & Law</a></li><li class="active js_toggle i-arrow-up" data-target=".breadcrumb-wrapper">Current debates on IHL</li></ol></div></section><section class="section-hero theme-brown"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-8"><h1 class="h1 font-xs-40 font-md-60">Current debates on IHL</h1><div class="topic-body font-xs-16 font-md-18"><p>Civilians are the main victims of IHL violations in today's conflicts. Contemporary conflict brings challenges for IHL in a number of areas, such as new technologies and the classification of conflicts. We must understand and respond to these challenges if IHL is to maintain its protective function.<br /><a class="btn" href="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/contemporary-challenges-ihl">read more</a></p></div></div><div class="col-md-4 hidden-xs hidden-sm"> <nav class="intro-menu font-xs-14 sans-serif"><h2 class="font-xs-16">In this section</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/participation-hostilities">Direct participation in hostilities</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/multinational-forces">Multinational forces</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/occupation">Occupation</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/privatization-war">Privatization of war </a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/respect-ihl">Respect for IHL</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/security-detention">Security detention</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/terrorism">Terrorism</a></li></ul> </nav></div></div></div><div class="navbar navbar--inline theme-brown hidden-md hidden-lg"> <a href="#" class="js_toggle navbar-toggle i-arrow-down-after">In this section</a> <nav id="js_continentSelection" class="clearfix toggle font-xs-12 font-md-14" role="navigation"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/participation-hostilities">Direct participation in hostilities</a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/multinational-forces">Multinational forces</a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/occupation">Occupation</a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/privatization-war">Privatization of war </a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/respect-ihl">Respect for IHL</a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/security-detention">Security detention</a> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/war-and-law/contemporary-challenges-for-ihl/terrorism">Terrorism</a> </nav></div> </section><section class="theme-brown vspace-top-small visible-xs visible-sm container"><div class="navbar navbar--switch"> <nav class="clearfix font-xs-12 js_toggle" data-target=".switch_container" data-settings='{"behaviour":"switch", "clickoutside":false}' role="navigation"> <a href="#" class="active col-xs-6" data-state="inactive">News</a> <a href="#" class="col-xs-6" data-state="active">Detail</a> </nav></div></section><section class="vspace-bottom vspace-top-small container"><div class="clearfix switch_mask row"><div class="switch_container"> <main class="col-xs-6 col-sm-6 col-md-8"><div class="theme-brown"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-6"><div class="thumbnail thumbnail-inner-caption "> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/icrc-report-ihl-and-challenges-contemporary-armed-conflicts" > <img src="https://www.icrc.org/sites/default/files/styles/country_banner/public/topic/banner_list/syrie_ligne_front_0.jpg?itok=PWldhz8F" alt="ICRC report on IHL and the challenges of contemporary armed conflicts" class="border-bottom" /> </a><div class="caption background-gradient"><p class="font-xs-18 font-sm-14 font-md-18"> <a h