eapons" class="label label-beige">Use of weapons</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/united-nations" class="label label-beige">United Nations</a></li></ul><ul class="list-label"><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/asia-pacific/india" class="label label-green">India</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/middle-east/israel-and-occupied-territories" class="label label-green">Israel and the occupied territories</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/europe-central-asia/switzerland" class="label label-green">Switzerland</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/americas/united-states-america" class="label label-green">United States of America</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/europe-central-asia/russian-federation" class="label label-green">Russian Federation</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/asia-pacific/australia" class="label label-green">Australia</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/europe-central-asia/belgium" class="label label-green">Belgium</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/europe-central-asia/united-kingdom" class="label label-green">United Kingdom</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/africa/ethiopia" class="label label-green">Ethiopia</a></li><li><a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/where-we-work/middle-east/syria" class="label label-green">Syria</a></li></ul></div></div> </aside></div></div></section><section class="clearfix bg-blue theme-blue"><div class="page-header page-header--lightline page-header--small"><h2 class="bg-blue h3">Photos &amp; videos</h2></div><div class="container vspace"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-landscape-6 col-sm-6 col-md-3"> <a href="https://www.icrc.org/en/document/webinar-counter-terrorism-sanctions-humanitarian-access-covid-19-era-0" class="thumbnail thumbnail-bottom-caption-inside caption-title-sm font-xs-14"> <img src="https://